com.example.kit.data.source

Class AbstractItemDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.kit.data.source.DataSource<Item,ItemSet>
      • com.example.kit.data.source.AbstractItemDataSource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ItemDataSource, TestItemDataSource

    public abstract class AbstractItemDataSource
extends DataSource<Item,ItemSet>
    Intermediate subclass of DataSource for ItemDataSources that need access to the Tag data sources to retrieve tag objects from the names. Necessary because there was a race condition when the tag datasource was not set explicitly after the construction of both types of data sources.
